Western Coal Advisory Autumn a benefit of membership in the Western Coal Council we are sending the latest issue of the Western Coal Advisory in pdf format Youll need Adobe Acrobat Reader to view this file This program is available at no charge at Acrobat Reader You will be receiving a printed version in about days We hope you enjoy receiving this copy in advance and thank you for your continued support of the Western Coal Council Janet Gellici Executive Director wwwwesterncoalcouncilorg If you do not wish to receive this newsletter in the future simply reply to this message with REMOVE in the subject area and we will remove your email address from future transmissions Thank You autumnpdf
